page.title: 02Where we come from.
page.content:
These are three family trees from boys of different nationalities from Form 12 at Winterbourne Junior Boys' School in July 1985.
My name is Hitesh Patel.I was born in Thornton Heath on the 5th March 1974. My dad was born in Dar-es-Salaam, Tanzania,East Africa.My mum was born in Dharmaj,Gujarat,India.My dad's mum was born in Virsad,Gujarat,India.My dad's father was born in Bhadran, Gujarat,India.My mum's mother was born in Nadiad,Gujarat,India.My mum's father was born in Dharmaj,Gujarat, India.
My name is Darren Sell.I was born in Norbury on the 19th March 1974.My dad, Norman Sell was born in East Fulham, London.My mum,Sandra was born in St. Mary's,North London.Contd.on page 3.
